      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 25 judgment</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 25 judgment</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>无妄，元亨，利貞。其匪正有眚，不利有攸往。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Wu Wang indicates great progress and success, while there will be advantage in being firm and correct. If (its subject and his action) be not correct, he will fall into errors, and it will not be advantageous for him to move in any direction.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="yijing-025-wu-wang__alignment-002">
      <prop type="x-work-id">yijing</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">yijing-025-wu-wang</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">section</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">block</prop>
