      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 25 六二</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 25 六二</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六二：不耕獲，不菑畬，則利有攸往。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second SIX, divided, shows one who reaps without having ploughed (that he might reap), and gathers the produce of his third year's fields without having cultivated them the first year for that end. To such a one there will be advantage in whatever direction he may move.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
