      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 25 九四</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 25 九四</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九四：可貞，无咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fourth NINE, undivided, shows (a case) in which, if its subject can remain firm and correct, there will be no error.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
