      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 25 九五</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 25 九五</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九五：无妄之疾，勿藥有喜。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fifth NINE, undivided, shows one who is free from insincerity, and yet has fallen ill. Let him not use medicine, and he will have occasion for joy (in his recovery).</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
