      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 25 上九</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 25 上九</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>上九：无妄，行有眚，无攸利。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The topmost NINE, undivided, shows its subject free from insincerity, yet sure to fall into error, if he take action. (His action) will not be advantageous in any way.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
